data.name: About
data.value:
This application has been implemented as a Thesis Project.
It aims to assist in the analysis of a file log captured by Snoopy Logger.
Author: María Yolanda González Castillo.
Tutor: Alejandro Calderón Mateos
Year implemented: 2015

data.name: BodyMail
data.value:
Dear Friend,
I am pleased to send you the requested reports .
Feel free to reuse the application for further analysis.
A greeting,
The Development Team
